              ],
              "variable": []
            },
            "description": "Validates the service's bootstrap token then returns the requested secret(s).\n\nTwo modes:\n- body.secret_name provided \u2192 single-secret mode: returns {\"value\": \"<plaintext>\"}\n- body.secret_name absent  \u2192 bulk mode (auth only): returns RS256 keypair dict",
